While waiting for the switches, I designed the PCB. The switches take up most of the board space, but there’s also some room for Microchip’s [AVR128DA64](https://ww1.microchip.com/downloads/aemDocuments/documents/MCU08/ProductDocuments/DataSheets/AVR128DA28-32-48-64-Data-Sheet-DS40002183.pdf) in the bottom left corner:

